Gollem. Gollem.

1
01:32:19,202 --> 01:32:20,661
Vlug.

1
01:32:22,664 --> 01:32:23,743
Hierheen.

1
01:32:26,460 --> 01:32:27,325
Kom.

1
01:32:27,586 --> 01:32:29,578
Kom op. Vlug.

1
